<span style="font-family:Whisper; font-size:52px; letter-spacing:3px;"> <center> I HATE MYSELF </center> </span>

[[A.A.E.G.|<span style="font-family:Whisper; font-size:11px; letter-spacing:3px;"> <center>~ Mathew </center> </span>]] </center> </span>


